'''議會宮'''（{{lang-ro|Palatul Parlamentului}}），又名'''共和國宮'''（{{lang|ro|Casa Republicii}}）、'''人民宮'''（{{lang|ro|Casa Poporului}}），是[[羅馬尼亞議會|羅馬尼亞議會]]的辦公地點，位於羅馬尼亞首都[[布加勒斯特|布加勒斯特]]{{link-en|繡線菊山|Dealul Spirii}}。議會宮高{{convert|84|m|ft}}，總樓面面積{{convert|365000|m2|sqft}}，體積{{convert|2550000|m3|cuft}}。議會宮重量達{{convert|4098500000|kg|e9lb e6t|2|abbr=off}}，被[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]認定為世界最重的建築<ref name="heavy">{{cite web|url=https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/heaviest-building/|title=Heaviest building|access-date=2021-03-29|work=Guinness World Records|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115225248/https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/heaviest-building/}}</ref>。

該建築由{{link-en|安卡·佩特雷斯庫|Anca Petrescu}}帶領的700人建築師團隊設計，工程耗時13年。建築外觀融合了[[社會主義現實主義|社會主義現實主義]]和現代[[新古典主義建築|新古典主義]]風格<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10421302/Anca-Petrescu.html|title=Anca Petrescu|access-date=2021-03-29|work=The Telegraph|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073045/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10421302/Anca-Petrescu.html}}</ref><ref name=":0" />。議會宮由[[羅馬尼亞社會主義共和國|羅馬尼亞共產黨執政時期]]領導人[[尼古拉·齐奥塞斯库|尼古拉·齐奥塞斯库]]下令修建<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://editiadedimineata.ro/megalomania-lui-ceausescu-dorinta-de-merge-pe-sub-bucuresti-si-povestea-catacombelor-secrete/|title=Megalomania lui Ceaușescu: dorința de a merge pe sub București și povestea catacombelor secrete|date=2018-06-11|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2021-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329125909/https://editiadedimineata.ro/megalomania-lui-ceausescu-dorinta-de-merge-pe-sub-bucuresti-si-povestea-catacombelor-secrete/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時羅馬尼亞國內對齐奥塞斯库本人和[[齐奥塞斯库家族|他家族]]的{{link-en|对齐奥塞斯库的个人崇拜|Nicolae Ceauşescu's cult of personality|個人崇拜}}日益升溫<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dcnews.ro/se-muncea-dar-se-si-murea-povesti-cutremuratoare-de-pe-santierele-lui-ceausescu_350347.html|title=Se muncea, dar se și murea. Povești cutremurătoare de pe șantierele lui Ceaușescu|date=2018-07-11|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711233600/https://www.dcnews.ro/se-muncea-dar-se-si-murea-povesti-cutremuratoare-de-pe-santierele-lui-ceausescu_350347.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

議會宮以其華麗的內部而著稱，建築由23個部分構成。[[羅馬尼亞參議院|羅馬尼亞參議院]]（{{lang|ro|Senat}}）和[[眾議院_(羅馬尼亞)|眾議院]]（{{lang|ro|Camera Deputaților}}）都在議會宮辦公。此外還有三座博物館和一個國際會議中心在議會宮辦公，包括{{link-en|國家當代藝術美術館 (羅馬尼亞)|National Museum of Contemporary Art (Romania)|國家當代藝術美術館}}、共產極權主義博物館（設立於2015年）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-politic-20444050-senatul-adoptat-legea-privind-infiintarea-muzeului-totalitarismului-comunist.htm |title=Senatul a adoptat legea privind infiintarea Muzeului Totalitarismului Comunist. Academia Romana va intocmi si un raport de condamnare a comunismului |work=HotNews.ro |date=2015-09-22 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162955/https://www.hotnews.ro/stiri-politic-20444050-senatul-adoptat-legea-privind-infiintarea-muzeului-totalitarismului-comunist.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>、宮殿博物館。雖然該建築最初和建設初期時的名稱是共和國宮，但在[[1989年羅馬尼亞革命|1989年羅馬尼亞革命]]之後，該建築被稱為人民宮。由於該建築醒目的特徵，眾多羅馬尼亞國家級活動和國際活動在這裡舉行。然而該建築仍有約70%的部分處於閒置狀態<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hotel-bucuresti.com/blog/2015/04/29/palatul-parlamentului-o-emblema-bucurestiului/ |title=Palatul Parlamentului, o emblema a Bucurestiului |work=Hotel-Bucuresti.com |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2015-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503002004/http://www.hotel-bucuresti.com/blog/2015/04/29/palatul-parlamentului-o-emblema-bucurestiului/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/12/05/travel/ceausescu-trail-bucharest-romania/index.html?hpt=hp_c5 |title=Palace of the damned dictator: On the trail of Ceausescu in Bucharest |work=CNN |author=John Malathronas |date=2014-12-05 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100122/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/12/05/travel/ceausescu-trail-bucharest-romania/index.html?hpt=hp_c5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{As of|2008}}，議會宮的工程費用達30億歐元，是世界最昂貴的政府建築<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gandul.info/stiri/casa-poporului-de-trei-ori-in-cartea-recordurilor-video-2521487 |title=Casa Poporului - de trei ori în Cartea Recordurilor |work=Gândul |date=2008-04-04 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2018-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727144519/http://www.gandul.info/stiri/casa-poporului-de-trei-ori-in-cartea-recordurilor-video-2521487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。議會宮每年的供暖、電力和照明費用超過600萬美元，可以和一座中型城市的電力費用相當<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.natgeo.ro/articole/istorie/8730-palatul-parlamentului-din-casa-poporului?showall=1 |title=Palatul Parlamentului din Casa Poporului |work=National Geographic România |author=Andrei Pandele |date=2009-04-29 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323140727/https://www.natgeo.ro/articole/istorie/8730-palatul-parlamentului-din-casa-poporului?showall=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Nicolae_Ceaușescu.jpg|thumb]]下令修建一座巨型建築]] 
[[File:EPP_Congress_2361_(8096737560).jpg|thumb]]

議會宮的建設是[[尼古拉·齐奥塞斯库|尼古拉·齐奥塞斯库]]對羅馬尼亞實施{{link-en|系統化政策|Systematization (Romania)}}的最極端體現。系統化是齐奥塞斯库在1971年訪問[[東亞|東亞]]時在[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鲜民主主义人民共和国]]接觸[[主體思想|主體思想]]後在羅馬尼亞實施的[[城市規劃|城市規劃]]政策。自1930年代[[卡羅爾二世|卡羅爾二世]]執政時期開始，羅馬尼亞就有重整議會宮所在地區市容的計劃。[[1977年布加勒斯特地震|1977年布加勒斯特地震]]為齐奥塞斯库提供了拆除布加勒斯特老舊部分的理由<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.muzeuldefotografie.ro/2013/09/demolarea-casei-grigore-cerkez-dupa-cutremurul-din-1977/|title=Demolarea casei Grigore Cerkez după cutremurul din 1977|date=2018-07-11|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711223246/https://www.muzeuldefotografie.ro/2013/09/demolarea-casei-grigore-cerkez-dupa-cutremurul-din-1977/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他希望在布加勒斯特建設一個符合該國政治立場的公民中心，並開始了基於社會主義現實主義的布加勒斯特重建計劃<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://pavilionmagazine.org/vlad-bodogan-architecture-of-oppression-an-analyses-of-the-socio-political-implications-behind-the-construction-of-casa-scanteii/|title=Vlad Bodogan: Architecture of oppression: an analyses of the socio-political implications behind the construction of Casa Scânteii|date=2018-07-11|website=Pavilion Magazine|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712004306/http://pavilionmagazine.org/vlad-bodogan-architecture-of-oppression-an-analyses-of-the-socio-political-implications-behind-the-construction-of-casa-scanteii/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。共和國宮是齐奥塞斯库計劃的核心。他的計劃開始於1978年，最初的目標是建設一個朝鮮首都[[平壤|平壤]]的複製品。

在經過公開競爭之後，{{link-en|安卡·佩特雷斯庫|Anca Petrescu}}被指定為這一項目的領導者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Stiri/De+la+Casa+Poporului+la+Palatul+Parlamentului+Istoria+cladirii+c |title=De la Casa Poporului la Palatul Parlamentului. Istoria clădirii care a intrat de trei ori în Cartea Recordurilor |work=Digi24 |date=2013-10-31 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305222611/http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Stiri/De+la+Casa+Poporului+la+Palatul+Parlamentului+Istoria+cladirii+c |dead-url=no }}</ref>。共和國宮的工程開始於1984年6月25日，齐奥塞斯库出席了開工儀式，並經常視察工程進展。

為修建共和國宮，烏拉納斯山（Uranus Hill）被夷為平地。該地區曾經建有國家檔案館、{{link-en|米哈伊·沃達修道院|Mihai Vodă Monastery}}等修道院，以及布蘭肯文斯（Brâncovenesc）醫院<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ziarulring.ro/stiri/12421/spitalul-brancovenesc-nu-trebuia-sa-cada |title=Spitalul Brâncovenesc nu trebuia să cadă! |work=Ziarul Ring |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2017-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428195619/http://www.ziarulring.ro/stiri/12421/spitalul-brancovenesc-nu-trebuia-sa-cada |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外這裡還曾有約37座工廠和作坊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metropotam.ro/Locuri-de-vizitat/Atunci-si-acum-Casa-Poporului-art5172725370/ |title=Atunci si acum: Casa Poporului |work=Metropotam |date=2009-06-09 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621191333/http://metropotam.ro/Locuri-de-vizitat/Atunci-si-acum-Casa-Poporului-art5172725370/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拆除工程開始於1982年，面積約{{convert|7|km2}}的舊市中心被拆除，約4萬人搬離該地區<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.radionetherlandsarchives.org/the-palace/ |title=The Palace of the Parliament in Bucharest |work=MRadio Netherlands Archives|date=1997-11-19}}</ref>。這些工作由軍人的義務勞動完成，以最小化成本<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.humanitas.ro/humanitas/robi-pe-uranus-0 |title=Robi pe Uranus |date=1992 |edition=I |isbn=973-28-0304-5 |author=Ioan Popa |publisher=Humanitas |access-date=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217011237/http://www.humanitas.ro/humanitas/robi-pe-uranus-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有2萬至10萬人參與了共和國宮工程，實施了三班倒。工人中有5000人是{{link-en|羅馬尼亞人民軍|Romanian People's Army}}的成員，還有眾多「志工」參加<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://adevarul.ro/locale/piatra-neamt/povesti-santierele-groazei-s-au-construit-sange-mastodontii-doriti-ceausescu-casa-poporului-canal-transfagarasan-bicaz-1_5520dd39448e03c0fd3b597d/index.html|title=Şantierele groazei. Cum s-au construit cu sânge mastodonţii doriţi de Ceauşescu: Casa Poporului, Canal, Transfăgărăşan şi Bicaz|date=2018-07-11|accessdate=2021-03-29|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126123149/https://adevarul.ro/locale/piatra-neamt/povesti-santierele-groazei-s-au-construit-sange-mastodontii-doriti-ceausescu-casa-poporului-canal-transfagarasan-bicaz-1_5520dd39448e03c0fd3b597d/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1989年時，該建築的成本估計有17.5億美元。2006年，這一數字是30億歐元。1990年，澳洲媒體大亨[[鲁伯特·默多克|鲁伯特·默多克]]試圖以10億美元的價格購買這座建築，但被拒絕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/romania-pitoreasca/ce-mesaje-ascunse-au-lasat-muncitorii-pe-zidurile-casei-poporului-detalii-nestiute.html |title=Detalii nestiute despre Casa Poporului, cea mai scumpa cladire administrativa din lume |work=Stirile Pro TV |date=2013-05-16 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119090112/https://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/romania-pitoreasca/ce-mesaje-ascunse-au-lasat-muncitorii-pe-zidurile-casei-poporului-detalii-nestiute.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 1989年之後 ===
1994年開始，議會宮是羅馬尼亞議會眾議院的辦公地點。眾議院之前在[[國會宮_(布加勒斯特)|國會宮]]辦公，但後來捐贈給[[羅馬尼亞正教會|羅馬尼亞正教會]]。2004年開始，羅馬尼亞參議院也從前[[羅馬尼亞共產黨|羅馬尼亞共產黨]]總部搬遷至議會宮辦公。在竣工6年後的2003年至2004年時，議會宮在外側電梯加裝了玻璃附件，以便於外界進入國家當代藝術美術館<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.ashgate.com/isbn/9780754670223 |title=Cultural Landscapes of Post-Socialist Cities |author=Mariusz Czepczynski |publisher=Ashgate |date=June 2008 |isbn=978-0-7546-7022-3 |access-date=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2015-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226134027/http://www.ashgate.com/isbn/9780754670223 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

議會宮內有一家僅服務政治家的餐廳。1998年開始，議會宮是{{link-en|東南歐合作倡議|Southeast European Cooperative Initiative}}（SECI）的辦公地點<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/foreign-policy/eu/regional-initiatives/seci |title=South-East Europe Cooperative Initiative (SECI) |work=Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Serbia |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151102070453/http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/foreign-policy/eu/regional-initiatives/seci |archive-date=2015-11-02 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2008年，議會宮舉辦了[[北大西洋公約組織|北大西洋公約組織]]（NATO）第20屆峰會。2010年，政治家{{link-en|席爾維·普利戈亞納|Silviu Prigoană}}建議將議會宮改建為購物中心和娛樂設施。他表示羅馬尼亞議會僅適用了這座建築30%的空間，因此應搬遷至其他建築內。雖然這一提案在羅馬尼亞引起爭論，政治家{{link-en|米隆·米特雷亞|Miron Mitrea}}駁斥稱這一想法是「兒戲」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/romania/7148097/Nicolae-Ceausescu-palace-to-be-turned-into-shopping-mall.html |title=Nicolae Ceausescu palace 'to be turned into shopping mall' |work=The Telegraph |author=Matthew Day |date=2010-02-04 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2019-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126023338/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/romania/7148097/Nicolae-Ceausescu-palace-to-be-turned-into-shopping-mall.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

議會宮也是眾多賽車賽事的場地，包括2011年的羅馬尼亞漂移大獎賽<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.speedhunters.com/2011/10/guest_blog_drift_ro_gt_gt_sideways_in_romania_s_capital_b/|title=Guest Blog: Drift.ro>> Sideways in Romania's Capital - Speedhunters|date=29 October 2011|work=Speedhunters|access-date=2018-02-13|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605053201/http://www.speedhunters.com/2011/10/guest_blog_drift_ro_gt_gt_sideways_in_romania_s_capital_b/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 建築圖片版權 ====
雖然議會宮的建築費用由公共財政負擔，且建築家亦並非受僱設計這座建築，但在首席設計師安卡·佩特雷斯庫去世之後，他的繼承人狀告羅馬尼亞眾議院未經許可就使用議會宮的圖像。眾議院還因出售帶有議會宮的照片和紀念品而被指控侵犯版權<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/familia-arhitectei-casei-poporului-vrea-2-din-castigurile-pe-care-camera-deputatilor-le-incaseaza.html|title=Bătălia pentru imaginea Palatului Parlamentului. Decizia luată de OSIM|work=Stirileprotv.ro|access-date=2018-11-02|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109012104/https://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/actualitate/familia-arhitectei-casei-poporului-vrea-2-din-castigurile-pe-care-camera-deputatilor-le-incaseaza.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite news |url=https://pandects.dpvue.com/2018/10/taking-photos-of-palace-of-parliament.html |title=Taking photos of the Palace of Parliament can be considered illegal |website=Pandects dpVUE |access-date=2018-11-02 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126012836/https://pandects.dpvue.com/2018/10/taking-photos-of-palace-of-parliament.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。法律專家指出，遊客因非商業用途而對建築進行拍攝並不受到限制<ref name=":2" />。佩特雷斯庫的繼承人則要求對議會宮圖片的任何商業用途需繳納2%的版權使用費<ref name=":1" />。

== 技術細節 ==
議會宮的工程開始於1984年，最初計劃在兩年內竣工。建築有八個地下層，最深的一層是一個核掩體，並通過一個長{{convert|20|km|mi|1}}的隧道連接羅馬尼亞主要政府機構<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.libertatea.ro/detalii/articol/secretele-casei-poporului-ceausescu-voia-sa-umble-cu-masina-pe-sub-bucuresti-323291.html |title=Secretele Casei Poporului {{!}} "Ceauşescu voia să umble cu maşina pe sub Bucureşti" |work=Libertatea |date=2011-02-21 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2016-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118225949/http://www.libertatea.ro/detalii/articol/secretele-casei-poporului-ceausescu-voia-sa-umble-cu-masina-pe-sub-bucuresti-323291.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

議會宮的總樓面面積達{{convert|365,000|m2|sqft}}，是世界第三大政府建築，僅次於[[美國|美國]]的[[五角大樓|五角大樓]]和[[曼谷|曼谷]]的{{link-en|泰國國會大樓|Sappaya-Sapasathan}}。該建築也是世界體積最大的建築，體積達{{convert|2,550,000|m3|cuft}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://adevarul.ro/news/bucuresti/la-plimbare-subsolul-casei-poporului-1_50bde9db7c42d5a663cfdab4/index.html |title=La plimbare prin subsolul Casei Poporului |work=Adevărul |date=2010-03-26 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2015-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226041248/http://adevarul.ro/news/bucuresti/la-plimbare-subsolul-casei-poporului-1_50bde9db7c42d5a663cfdab4/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，比[[吉薩大金字塔|吉薩大金字塔]]多2%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metropotam.ro/Locuri-de-vizitat/lucruri-mai-putin-stiute-despre-casa-poporului-cea-mai-mare-cladire-din-europa-art3946701317/ |title=Lucruri mai putin stiute despre Casa Poporului - cea mai mare cladire din Europa |work=Metropotam |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721151959/http://metropotam.ro/Locuri-de-vizitat/lucruri-mai-putin-stiute-despre-casa-poporului-cea-mai-mare-cladire-din-europa-art3946701317 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.travelworld.ro/atractii-romania/arhitectura/casa-poporului.html |title=Casa Poporului |work=TravelWorld.ro |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2019-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907232415/http://www.travelworld.ro/atractii-romania/arhitectura/casa-poporului.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於其龐大的重量，議會宮每年下沉{{convert|6|mm|in}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gandul.info/magazin/casa-poporului-se-scufunda-in-sol-in-fiecare-an-ce-spun-specialistii-despre-acest-fenomen-13739642 |title=Casa Poporului se scufundă în sol în fiecare an. Ce spun specialiştii despre acest "fenomen" |work=Gândul |date=2014-12-26 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2018-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726104549/http://www.gandul.info/magazin/casa-poporului-se-scufunda-in-sol-in-fiecare-an-ce-spun-specialistii-despre-acest-fenomen-13739642 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 材料 ===
議會宮的幾乎全部材料都取自於羅馬尼亞國內。少數例外之一是{{link-en|尼古拉·伯爾切斯庫|Nicolae Bălcescu}}廳的大門。這座門是齐奥塞斯库的朋友，曾長期擔任[[薩伊|薩伊]]總統[[蒙博托·塞塞·塞科|蒙博托·塞塞·塞科]]贈送的禮物<ref name="amazing places">{{cite web |url=http://www.youramazingplaces.com/palace-of-the-parliament-bucharest/ |title=7 Amazing Facts about The Palace of The Parliament in Bucharest |work=YourAmazingPlaces.com |accessdate=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812042440/http://www.youramazingplaces.com/palace-of-the-parliament-bucharest/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

議會宮使用了3,500噸[[鉛玻璃|水晶]]，用於製造480個[[枝形吊燈|枝形吊燈]]、1409個天花板燈和镜子。議會宮還使用了70萬噸鋼和銅，用於製作門窗、吊燈和[[柱頭_(建築)|柱頭]]。大理石用量達{{convert|1000000|m3}}<ref name="amazing places" />，木材用量達{{convert|900000|m3}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.casapoporului.ro/article/264/Casa-Poporului |title=Casa Poporului |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208052622/http://www.casapoporului.ro/article/264/Casa-Poporului |archive-date=2015-12-08 |accessdate=2021-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

